{"TopicId":137711,"ForumId":29,"TopicTitle":"Message Placement","CreatedByName":"Warezcrawler","CreatedById":145377,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-22T12:27:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Warezcrawler","CreatedById":145377,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-22T12:27:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes anybody know if it\u0027s possible to move where KSP writes it messages on screen? Like the one for when transmitting science back to Kerbin? And when saving etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, how does one create custom messages for when the user uses my mod?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aelfhe1m","CreatedById":142910,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-22T14:09:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nScreenMessages.PostScreenMessage(\u0022message\u0022, 3f, ScreenMessageStyle.UPPER_LEFT);\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMiddle parameter is duration. There are other overloads with various options.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-22T14:10:23Z\u0022 title=\u002204/22/2016 02:10  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 22, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Aelfhe1m\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Warezcrawler","CreatedById":145377,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-22T14:41:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222530695\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022137711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461334178\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022142910\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Aelfhe1m\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n38 minutes ago, Aelfhe1m said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote